      <title>地方选举惨败后，保守党敦促苏纳克转向右翼</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-05/tories-press-sunak-to-move-to-right-after-local-election-rout</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国首相里希·苏纳克面临着保守党议员要求采取移民上限的呼吁，因为在上周的地方选举中，他的政党被击败后，他面临着要求其进一步右倾的压力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-05/tories-press-sunak-to-move-to-right-after-local-election-rout</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 05 May 2024 23:01:00 GMT</pubDate>
