      <title>卢拉访问巴西南部 数十人在洪水中失踪</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-05/lula-visits-southern-brazil-with-dozens-missing-in-record-floods</link>
      <description><![CDATA[巴西总统路易斯·伊纳西奥·卢拉·达席尔瓦和主要内阁成员周日抵达该国南部，那里破纪录的洪水导致一个主要机场关闭，社区被淹没，造成数十人死亡，多人失踪。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-05/lula-visits-southern-brazil-with-dozens-missing-in-record-floods</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 05 May 2024 16:31:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
